		        API's
----------------------------------
Member Registration(post method)
1) http://rms.chickdairsfjhighschool.edu.bd/api/members

// Login(post method)
2) http://rms.chickdairsfjhighschool.edu.bd/api/login/

//Comments(post method)
3) http://rms.chickdairsfjhighschool.edu.bd/api/comments/

//Reports(post method)
4) http://rms.chickdairsfjhighschool.edu.bd/api/reports/

//Get All Comments Of a member (Post method.  pass a param named member_id)
5)http://rms.chickdairsfjhighschool.edu.bd/api/previous_comments

//Get all comments for a task of a memeber (Post method.  pass  params named member_id, task_id)
6)http://rms.chickdairsfjhighschool.edu.bd/api/previous_comments_of_a_task

//Get all comments of a task (Post method.  pass a param named task_id)
7)http://rms.chickdairsfjhighschool.edu.bd/api/comments_of_a_task

//Get All Reports of a constructor (Post method.  pass a param named constructor_id)
8)http://rms.chickdairsfjhighschool.edu.bd/api/all_reports

//Get All Finished Task List of a constructor (Post method.  pass a param named constructor_id)
9)http://rms.chickdairsfjhighschool.edu.bd/api/all_finished_task

//Get All Pending Task List of a constructor (Post method.  pass a param named constructor_id)
10)http://rms.chickdairsfjhighschool.edu.bd/api/all_pending_task

//Submit a task if successfully completed (Post method.  pass a params named constructor_id, task_id)
11) http://rms.chickdairsfjhighschool.edu.bd/api/task_done

